Lore

Deliverance Node is a visual record of an emergent network.

Each Node begins with a core and expands through a series of connections, pathways and signals. Over time, simple interactions produce increasingly complex structures.

Some Nodes develop sparse networks.

Others become densely interconnected systems.

The resulting patterns are not designed by hand. They emerge from the underlying rules that govern the network.

Every Deliverance Node captures one possible state of that system.
